[{"Id": 1016372, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 1, "EnglishDescription": "From Hasan bin Mith'lah: our master the leader of the time (a) said: \"Tell people to dignify the place and offer 4 rakat of prayer, 2 rakat for salutation of the Mosque as follows: In every rakat after <Surah Fateha> once, recite <Surah Ikhlaas> 7 times, offer the glorification in Ruku and Sujood 7 times.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Janabe Hasan bin Mislah Jamkarani likhte hai, Imam-e-Zamana (a) ne farmaya keh logo’n se kaho keh us makaan ki taraf ziyadah raghbat kare’n, us jagah ka ehteraam kare us makaan mein 4 rakat namaz padhe, 2 rakat Tahyeh (Ehteraam) Masjid jiski har rakat mein 1 martaba <Surah Fateha> ke baad 100 martaba <Surah Ikhlaas> padhe aur 7 martaba har Ruku mein zikr-e-Ruku aur Sajdeh mein zikr-e-Sajdah padhe.", "UrduDescription": "جناب حسن بن مثلہ جمکرانی لکھتے ہیں کہ امام زمان نے فرمایا کہ لوگوں سے کہو کہ اس مکان کی طرف زیادہ رغبت کریں اس جگہ کا احترام کریں اس مکان میں ۴ رکعت نماز پڑھیں، ۲ رکعت تحیہ مسجد کہ ہر رکعت میں ایک مرتبہ <سورۂ فاتحہ> اور ۱۰۰ مرتبہ <سورۂ اخلاص> کو پڑھے اور ہر رکوع اور سجدہ میں ۷ مرتبہ ذکر پڑھے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1002626, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "All glory be to Allah; all praise be to Allah; there is no god save Allah; Allah is the Greatest.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Allah paak hai. Allah hi ke liye hamd hai. Nahi koi ma’bood siwaaye Allah ke aur Allah buzurg-tar hai.", "Urdu": "پاک ہے اﷲاور حمد اﷲہی کے لئے ہے اور اﷲکے سوا کوئی معبودنہیں اور اﷲبزرگ تر ہے۔", "RArabic": "SUBHAANALLAHE WAL HAMDO LILLAAHE WA-LA ILAAHA ILLALLAAHO WALLAAHO AKBAR.", "ArabicText1": "سُبْحَانَ اللہِ وَالْحَمْدُ لِلہِ وَلَا اِلٰہَ اِلَّا اللہُ وَاللہُ اَكْبَرُ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016373, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": 2, "EnglishDescription": "The other 2 rakats of prayer should be offer for the Imam of the time (a) as follows: In every rakat recite <Surah Fateha> when you reach the verse “IYYAA-KA NA’BODOO WA IYYAA-KA NASTA-EE’N” you repeat the verse for 100 times, then you complete the remaining verse of the Surah, you will glorify Allah for 7 times in Ruku and Sujood position. After namaz recite Tasbeeh-e-Zahra and then go in Sajdah and recite salawaat on Muhammad (s) and his Progeny (a) for 100 times. Whoever observes this namaz is like he has prayed in the sacred house of Kaaba.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Aur 2 rakat namaz Sahebaz Zamaan (a) ki niyyat se adaa kare keh jiski har rakat mein <Surah Fateha> padhe to jab aayat “IYYAA-KA NA’BODOO WA IYYAA-KA NASTA-EE’N” par pohonche to usey 100 martaba padhe aur surah tamaam karne ke baad Ruku mein ja kar 7 martaba Zikr-e-Ruku aur Sajdeh mein zikr-e-Sajdah padhe. Baad az Namaz Tasbeeh-e-Zahra (s) padhe aur phir sajdeh mein ja kar 100 martaba Muhammad (s) aur unki Aal (a) par salawaat bheje. Jo bhi yeh namaz ko anjaam dega goya aisa hai keh us ne Kaabe mein namaz padhi hai.", "UrduDescription": "اور ۲ رکعت نماز صاحب الزمان پڑھے اس ترتیب سے <سورۂ فاتحہ> پڑھے اور جب (ایّاک نعبد و ایاک نستعین) پر پہنچے تو اس کو ۱۰۰ مرتبہ پڑھے جب نماز تمام کرے تو تھیلیل کہے اور حضرت فاطمہ الزھراؑ کی تسبیح پڑھے جب تسبیح تمام کرے تو ۱۰۰ مرتبہ محمد و آل محمد پر درود بھیجے جو بھی یہ نماز پڑھے گویا ایسا ہے کہ اس نے کعبہ میں نماز پڑھی ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicTex